These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: time-travel, horror
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, april
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, taxi
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person watching horror movies is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | horror    | time-travel |
| Birthday         | april | january    |
| Transport     | roller     | taxi      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: potato, spinach
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, traveling
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, train
1. the person driving the train is on the left of the person eating potato##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Food      | spinach  | potato   |
| Hobby   | traveling | puzzles  |
| Transport     | train   | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, february
House: futuristic, art-deco
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, swimming
1. the person who's birthday is in february is in an even position##4
2. the futuristic house is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Birthday         | september   | february  |
| House   | art-deco | futuristic  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey   | swimming |

