.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, singing
2 different games are played: bridge, mah-jongg
2 different pets are kept: mouse, pony
1. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
2. the owner of the mouse is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby         | fishing    | singing    |
| Game   | mah-jongg     | bridge      |
| Pet         | mouse | pony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: pepper, radish
There are 2 different favourite colors: lavender, turquise
There are 2 different nationalities: indian, egyptian
1. the egyptian is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
2. the indian is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
3. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | radish | pepper     |
| Color     | turquise | lavender |
| Nationality   | egyptian | indian    |

 #################################

 
