.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-10::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, oliveros
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, frog
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, singing
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2    |
| Cigar   | oliveros | bolivar     |
| Pet       | frog        | guinea-pig    |
| Hobby      | filmmaking  | singing |

