The people prefer 2 different music-genres: funk, pop
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, ship
1. the fan of pop is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
2. the fan of pop is in an odd position##4
3. the fan of funk is on the right of the person eating peas##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Food           | peas     | tomato |
| Music-Genre   | pop | funk  |
| Transport     | ship      | boat |

