.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, biathlon
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, indian
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, amaryllis
1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
2. the colombian is on the left of the indian##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Sport         | biathlon | rugby |
| Nationality   | colombian     | indian     |
| Flower           | amaryllis          | dahlia     |

